{"TopicId":187338,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"KSP2 Hype Train Thread","CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T20:46:45Z","PageNum":160,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:14:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229157\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675806169\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ninvested a lot of money in not spending money.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSmart - they already probably have a ton of EA pre-orders and all of us just waiting around for it to drop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoney saved on marketing and hype can go other places.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd - Sandbagging is okay by me.\u00A0 \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003EI\u0027m the kind of guy who won\u0027t watch trailers for movies I\u0027m excited about.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675806701\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022107350\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SolarAdmiral\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, SolarAdmiral said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey this is a great find! I also missed this. Though I got a little more excited at first thinking you meant the huge fuel refineries they showed off were confirmed to be able to be mounted and moved. Hopefully they are, I want to build an absolutely massive mobile base.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt will be interesting to see if anything is restricted to colonies or ships. Like, could we build a massive mobile space colony? Can ships be built at other bigger ships, can the orbital construction yard be put on a suitably massive ship? Can we build a version of the Homeworld Mothership or an Eldar Craftworld to explore other systems? What does the line between spaceship, spacestation, and orbital colony look like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe interesting parts for me is that (at least the size shown) can be mounted \u0027to later engines\u0027 needed to fly them around... meaning heavy.\u00A0 But the part that stands out is\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675805835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n37 minutes ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nstructural foundation parts that can be attached to the bottoms of colony parts - they work similarly to launch clamps in the original KSP, with height automatically adjusting to reach the ground. The player has full control over them - they come in a range of types and sizes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat will make Colonies quite interesting to look at - fer shure!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SolarAdmiral","CreatedById":107350,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:22:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229170\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675808069\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe interesting parts for me is that (at least the size shown) can be mounted \u0027to later engines\u0027 needed to fly them around... meaning heavy.\u00A0 But the part that stands out is\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI mean that might be slightly an exaggeration. For places like the Mun or Minimus, you can move just about anything with enough poodles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stephensan","CreatedById":222320,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:26:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229170\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675808069\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEA pre-orders\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nzero preorders.. you start to purchase on date of beta\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:27:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675808808\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022222320\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stephensan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Stephensan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nzero preorders.. you start to purchase on date of beta\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nObviously. They are saying that it is essentially the same thing as a preorder for that group.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:28:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh and by the way, rewatch this video. It has important KSP2 information that a lot of people forgot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Yp1zAfjfIW4?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Kerbal Space Program 2: The Science Secrets of the Reveal Trailer - IGN First\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:33:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome comments removed. Keep it on-topic, please, and if you are tired of \u0022certain\u0022 \u0022toxic\u0022 people, why not set them to ignore and never be bothered by them again? Posting to reply to them merely means you spend more time on something you consider unpleasant.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BowlerHatGuy3","CreatedById":222738,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:35:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675800114\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212496\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022poopslayer78\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, poopslayer78 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew screenshot from Discord\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExplosions!!!!!! \u0026gt;:)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T22:36:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675805835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n56 minutes ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBig colony extractors can be wheeled around?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd that thing they\u0027re showing is just the \u003Cem\u003Escanner.\u00A0\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nirgal","CreatedById":211448,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T23:09:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229179\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675808935\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh and by the way, rewatch this video. It has important KSP2 information that a lot of people forgot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Yp1zAfjfIW4?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Kerbal Space Program 2: The Science Secrets of the Reveal Trailer - IGN First\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome things I hadn\u0027t known, or forgotten about:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nIce falling off fuel tanks during launch\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCountdown to launch (skippable)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAxial tilt of celestial bodies (nice)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nKerbals are not afraid to break the law (nukes in space breaking partial test ban treaty of 1963)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSpring 2020 release date (sorry it\u0027s funny to include irrelevant bullet points to me)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-07T23:22:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675811384\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211448\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nirgal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, Nirgal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals are not afraid to break the law (nukes in space breaking partial test ban treaty of 1963)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuman laws don\u0027t pertain to Kerbals.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TLTay","CreatedById":184633,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T00:15:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675800114\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212496\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022poopslayer78\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, poopslayer78 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew screenshot from Discord\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is some quality work, no sarcasm. That looks fantastic. Some more bright light from the blast might be the only suggestion I can think of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"b0054254","CreatedById":225329,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:02:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675800114\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212496\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022poopslayer78\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, poopslayer78 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew screenshot from Discord\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022kerbonoooooo.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1039972362117988353/1072581416447131658/kerbonoooooo.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0That explosion looks much better than anything I\u0027ve ever seen in KSP 1, does look a bit 2-D however, but could just be nature of this specific explosion occurring in the flame trench perhaps?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso have we seen those specific tanks that are falling down before, Colony parts maybe?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:15:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229179\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675808935\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt has important KSP2 information that a lot of people forgot\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you may be reading too much into this.\u00A0 The release trailer was a film.\u00A0 Not gameplay.\u00A0 Nothing (like ice dropping from the rocket) was promised.\u00A0 It just looks cool.\u00A0 Not to say it won\u0027t be in game - but puffery and hype... Not a promise.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675811384\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211448\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nirgal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Nirgal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAxial tilt of celestial bodies (nice)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOutside the Kerbolar System.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:25:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229236\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675818951\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154477\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JoeSchmuckatelli\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, JoeSchmuckatelli said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOutside the Kerbolar System.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would still like to see just a bit of it inside the Kerbolar system. Keep kerbin and its moons the same, but if Gilly and Vall had a bit of tilt? Might make a nice introduction to the problem.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MARL_Mk1","CreatedById":192535,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:44:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hadn\u0027t noticed this at first...\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nDo you guys remember that KSP1 bug where terrain texture would just... \u0022pixelate\u0022 and show up as small defined pixel-like grid squares?\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nOh, well.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022MpeYUbE.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002249.25\u0022 height=\u0022571\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/MpeYUbE.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:45:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConveniently cropped the important text\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MARL_Mk1","CreatedById":192535,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T01:57:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229255\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675820721\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConveniently cropped the important text\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot cropping anything on purpose or with any nefarious intentions.\u00A0Just pointing it out.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe other very recent screenshot we got on Twitter showing a very close-up view of the terrain (with confirmed Low settings by the devs) \u003Cstrong\u003Edoesn\u0027t show these artifacts\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m just expecting to not have these same decade-old texture issues happen on KSP2 aswell.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8759076582\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=https://twitter.com/KerbalSpaceP/status/1622641284551671810\u0022 style=\u0022height:764px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd no, hiding behind \u0022Beta\u0022 \u003Cstrong\u003Eif\u003C/strong\u003E issues like these arise on the release build for the mere fact of the game being on the Early Access program won\u0027t be a credible excuse, since EA is only supposed to exist to not hold the remaining content back after a normal release, according to PD\u0027s Senior Marketing Manager on his most recent interview.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-08T02:05:14Z\u0022 title=\u002202/08/2023 02:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 8, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by MARL_Mk1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BowlerHatGuy3","CreatedById":222738,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T02:08:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229215\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675815359\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184633\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TLTay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, TLTay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is some quality work, no sarcasm. That looks fantastic. Some more bright light from the blast might be the only suggestion I can think of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf the explosion is big enough create a shockwave that destroys everything within a few kilometers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T02:09:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re 16 days from release build, a lot can happen in that time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BowlerHatGuy3","CreatedById":222738,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T02:13:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675822165\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re 16 days from release build, a lot can happen in that time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEhh I don\u2019t know about that. I\u2019ve lost too much trust in game developers to consider that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T02:26:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229266\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675822165\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re 16 days from release build, a lot can happen in that time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe best way for them to get a \u0027wow\u0027 out of this crowd is to be actually sandbagging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope they don\u0027t stop if they are.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf not; my wallet remains ready.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T02:55:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229199\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675812137\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113880\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022shdwlrd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, shdwlrd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuman laws don\u0027t pertain to Kerbals.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis, as I imagine kerbals to be way more peaceful but I imagine they banned nuclear bombs in the atmosphere because of broken windows and fallout.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe city wanted firework and detonating this test nuclear bomb will give valuable insight in nuclear fusion.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T06:14:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229258\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675821424\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192535\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MARL_Mk1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, MARL_Mk1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsince EA is only supposed to exist to not hold the remaining content back after a normal release, according to PD\u0027s Senior Marketing Manager on his most recent interview.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone finally understands! Thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T06:50:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, I had a funny thought and figured I\u0027d share it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know why, but I imagined Intercept running through a go-no go poll before launch.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight just be my sleep deprived mind being silly, but still think it\u0027s funny.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and of course Nate Simpson is leading the poll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf they ever did truly do this, they should do an EA launch live stream and treat it like a space launch, T- counter and everything.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nT-minus... 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, go for store release, 3, 2, 1, and... lift off of Kerbal Space Program 2 into Early Access, marking a new decade in space sim flight!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nKSP 2 has cleared the tower!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-02-08T07:20:33Z\u0022 title=\u002202/08/2023 07:20  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 8, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by GoldForest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-08T07:21:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224229325\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675839046\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277770\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GoldForest\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, GoldForest said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, I had a funny thought and figured I\u0027d share it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know why, but I imagined Intercept running through a go-no go poll before launch.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight just be my sleep deprived mind being silly, but still think it\u0027s funny.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf, and of course Nate Simpson is leading the poll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf they ever did truly do this, they should do an EA launch live stream and treat like a space launch, T- counter and everything.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nT-minus... 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, go for store release, 3, 2, 1, and... lift off of Kerbal Space Program 2 into Early Access, marking a new decade in space sim flight!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 2 has cleared the tower!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224228269\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187338\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221675634629\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022219348\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vl3d\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/6/2023 at 12:03 AM, Vl3d said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis video represents the KSP2 Early Access launch so perfectly. Everything starting with the crash coming from KSP1, Jeb\u0027s face, demanding and upset attitude, the pirouette, the little trinkets that he brought to the Junkyard (suggestions on forum), the little confetti rocket (sneakpeaks)... to the hard work the engineer is doing, the money suitcase... the missing parachute, the panic, the running away, the door slam. The clouds!!! We\u0027re all going up whether we like it or not!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/54fDJKgjUrs?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Jeb\u0027s Junkyard\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}